---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  titulo="Proyectos Open Source · LRA Cloud Operations"
  descripcion="Herramientas open source de nivel producción e implementaciones de referencia por LRA Cloud Ops. Libres para usar, bifurcar y adaptar."
  keywords="open source DevOps, Kubernetes GitOps, Terraform AWS, gestión flota Linux, FastAPI Docker, agente Claude AI"
>
  <!-- ─── HERO ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #0A2540;">
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
      style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(147,184,255,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 28px 28px;"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none"
      style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 110%, rgba(30,111,255,0.2) 0%, transparent 65%);"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-5 sm:px-6 py-20 sm:py-28 text-center"
    >
      <span
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6"
        style="background: rgba(30,111,255,0.2); color: #93b8ff; border: 1px solid rgba(30,111,255,0.25);"
      >
        <svg
          class="w-3.5 h-3.5"
          fill="currentColor"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <path
            fill-rule="evenodd"
            clip-rule="evenodd"
            d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0112 6.844c.85.004 1.705.115 2.504.337 1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.019 10.019 0 0022 12.017C22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        Open Source
      </span>
      <h1
        class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6"
        style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;"
      >
        Proyectos Open Source
      </h1>
      <p
        class="text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-4"
        style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.8);"
      >
        Herramientas de nivel producción e implementaciones de referencia.
        Libres para usar, bifurcar y adaptar.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.5);">
        Licencia MIT &middot; github.com/lra-cloud-ops
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20" style="background: #F8FAFC;">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <!-- k8s-on-premise card -->
      <div
        class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200"
        style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-left: 4px solid #1E6FFF; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(10,37,64,0.04), 0 8px 32px rgba(10,37,64,0.09);"
      >
        <div
          class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between gap-4 mb-4"
        >
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div
              class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
              style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1E6FFF 0%, #1452cc 100%);"
            >
              <svg
                class="w-5 h-5 text-white"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  d="M5 12h14M5 12a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v4a2 2 0 01-2 2M5 12a2 2 0 00-2 2v4a2 2 0 002 2h14a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2m-7-9v18"
                ></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold" style="color: #0A2540;">
                k8s-on-premise
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">Kubernetes & GitOps</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span
              class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full"
              style="background: #EEF4FF; color: #1E6FFF; border: 1px solid #c3d9ff;"
              >En Desarrollo</span
            >
            <span
              class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full"
              style="background: #f0fdf4; color: #15803d; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;"
              >Activo</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-5" style="color: #334155;">
          Clúster Kubernetes de nivel producción sobre bare metal. Automatizado
          con Vagrant + VirtualBox + kubeadm. ArgoCD GitOps, NGINX Ingress,
          Calico CNI. Fase 3/18 — clúster completo desde cero con un solo
          comando: <code
            class="font-mono text-sm px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded"
            style="background: #EEF4FF; color: #1E6FFF;">vagrant up</code
          >.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
          {
            [
              'Kubernetes v1.31.14',
              'ArgoCD',
              'Helm v3.21.0',
              'Calico v3.27.0',
              'NGINX Ingress',
              'Vagrant',
              'VirtualBox',
            ].map((tag) => (
              <span
                class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full font-medium"
                style="background: #f8fafc; color: #475569; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;"
              >
                {tag}
              </span>
            ))
          }
        </div>

        <a
          href="https://github.com/lra-cloud-ops/k8s-on-premise"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl transition-all hover:opacity-90"
          style="background: #0A2540; color: white;"
        >
          <svg
            class="w-4 h-4"
            fill="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path
              fill-rule="evenodd"
              clip-rule="evenodd"
              d="M12 2C6.477 2 2 6.484 2 12.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0112 6.844c.85.004 1.705.115 2.504.337 1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.202 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.943.359.309.678.92.678 1.855 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.019 10.019 0 0022 12.017C22 6.484 17.522 2 12 2z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
          Ver en GitHub
