                aws-terraform-devops
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">
                Infraestructura Cloud & CI/CD
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span
              class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full"
              style="background: #f0fdf4; color: #15803d; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;"
              >Producción</span
            >
            <span
              class="text-xs font-semibold px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full"
              style="background: #f0fdf4; color: #15803d; border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;"
              >Activo</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed mb-5" style="color: #334155;">
          Infraestructura AWS lista para producción con Terraform modular. EKS +
          RDS Multi-AZ + CI/CD dual (GitHub Actions + Jenkins). Gates de calidad
          SonarCloud, estado remoto en S3 con bloqueo DynamoDB — sin
          credenciales estáticas mediante IAM OIDC.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
          {
            [
              'Terraform',
              'AWS EKS',
              'RDS PostgreSQL 15',
              'GitHub Actions',
              'Jenkins',
              'SonarCloud',
              'Flask',
              'Docker',
            ].map((tag) => (
              <span
                class="text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full font-medium"
                style="background: #f8fafc; color: #475569; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;"
              >
                {tag}
              </span>
